snippet.title: Reality Clash - Gameplay Experience
snippet.description:
Challenge your friends or fight bots in full AR combat.

Step through the Portal and enter a virtual battlefield known as ‘The Sim’ where your movement, reactions and strategy are crucial to your success.

Ios: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/reali...

Android: http://play.google.com/store/apps/det...

Check out our website: https://realityclash.com/

Check out our social channels:

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/realityclash/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/reality_clash

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheRealityClash
